rows.label: tlk400903_msg0005
rows.name:
Hmm... Weren't there some over there
the first time we came here?

rows.label: tlk400903_msg0006
rows.name:
Come to think of it, I do recall
something of that nature.

rows.label: tlk400903_msg0007
rows.name:
According to memory of Hana,
yellow barrels were definitely there.

rows.label: tlk400903_msg0008
rows.name:
So that means...someone must have
picked them up already?

rows.label: tlk400903_msg0009
rows.name: I can only assume as much.

rows.label: tlk400903_msg0010
rows.name: Well, that leaves us without any leads...

rows.label: tlk400903_msg0012
rows.name: Tora not about to give up so easy!

rows.label: tlk400903_msg0013
rows.name:
Tora remember there is junk shop in
Alba Margen. We ask for info there?

rows.label: tlk400903_msg0014
rows.name:
Another rare good suggestion
from Masterpon!

rows.label: tlk400903_msg0015
rows.name:
A junk shop, huh? Yeah, they might
know a thing or two about parts for
artificial Blades.
